<template>
    <VuePDF :pdf="pdf" :page="1" />
  </template>

<script>
import {usePDF, VuePDF} from 'VuePDF'

export default {
    components: {
      VuePDF
    },
    setup(){
      const { pdf, pages, info } = usePDF("/lab/backend/files/123_11:26:00.pdf")
      console.log(`Document has ${pages} pages`)
      console.log(`Document info: ${info}`)
      return {
        pdf
      }
    }
  }
</script>
